ALTER TABLE Settlements ADD COLUMN RevisionNumber   INTEGER DEFAULT 0;
ALTER TABLE Settlements ADD COLUMN FormulaVersion   INTEGER DEFAULT 0;
```

#### [NEW] `Services/SettlementIntegrityService.cs`
```csharp
